title: Spacious Lakes One Bedroom W/ Office, $50 off per Mo Promotion
posting_body: ['Uptown Main Level with Office Room, 0.5 Miles from Bde Maka Ska, Heat Paid, $50 Monthly Move In Special', 'Property Address', '3554 Emerson Ave S. - #7 | Minneapolis, MN 55408', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'This unit is ready for in person showings and move in.', 'Current photos and video walkthrough are located on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'Very spacious bedroom.', 'Office room is 9x10.', 'The unit has all new carpet.', '1 or 2 Year Lease.', '$50 off per month for the 1st lease term with any lease longer than 12 month.', 'Pets are welcome with positive rental reference and credit.', '(Dog fee $30mo, Cat fee $20mo)', 'Applications are available on the Guardian Property Management website.', 'Each application is $50 per adult and can be paid with a credit or debit card.', 'Application is based on income, credit history (Guardian Property Management will not use credit score but will be using information from your credit report), rental/work history and includes a criminal background check.', 'For full criteria visit our website and click “apply now” on the listed unit.', 'Any additional questions please call or email Billy.', 'Broker: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Agent:', 'Billy Sommers', 'Amenities', 'Office Space', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 850', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,175.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,175.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
